15
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:43,160
Hey, Fletcher.
How'd it go?

16
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:46,160
Just another victory for the
wrongly accused. - Yeah, right.

17
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:49,040
Mr. Reede, great job.
Do you want your coat back?

18
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:51,480
No, I'm sure you'll be
needing it again and again.

19
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:54,960
Do you have a moment? - I'm late.
It's my day to be with my son.

20
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:57,840
