to talk about your big win.

21
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,880
Yeah? How's my hair?

22
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,800
Fabulous.
You look great.

23
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:21,280
What time is it? - I am sure your
dad just got held up in court again.

24
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:31,360
Dad!
- Maximilian!

25
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:37,760
Hey, how ya doin', creep?

26
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,720
Good.

27
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:44,160
Me too, except my arm
has been botherin' me.

28
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,440
Oh, no, Dad!
- Oh, yeah.

29
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:49,280
