30
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:55,640
Nothing can stop the claw!

31
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:02,560
Run, boy, run!
Save yourself!

32
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:05,040
Do the claw to Mom!
Do the claw to Mom!

33
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:08,560
Uh-oh. You found
the claw's only weakness.

34
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:11,480
Subzero temperatures!

35
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:15,040
So, did you have any trouble
finding the place?

36
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:18,520
Okay, I'm late. I'm sorry.
I ran out of gas.

37
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:22,720
The gauge is broken.
Rough neighborhood too.

38
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,800
Good thing I was wearin'
neutral gang colors.

39
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:27,400
