to see wrestling!

44
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:42,360
Oh, Fletcher!
- Oh, Audrey!

45
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:45,240
Why do you have to take him
to see that stuff? It's very violent.

46
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:49,720
