to be a warrior.

47
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,680
Who better to guide him
than Rick Rude...

48
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:55,040
and Randy Macho-man Savage
in the cage of death?

49
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:59,120
Oh, good!

50
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:02,800
Jerry, how's it goin'?
- Hey, gipper!

51
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:05,080
