by the minute!

52
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:07,880
Fletcher, pleasure to see you.
Hi, honey!

53
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:10,280
Hi.

54
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:13,960
Wow. That was a nice image.
Deleted.

55
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:17,720
